# Privacy Policy

**Polly-App**  
Effective Date: February 17, 2026  
Contact: abrahamborg@gmail.com  
Website: https://github.com/Abe-Borg/Polly-App

---

## 1. Information We Collect

We collect phone numbers provided by users or authorized administrators for the purpose of sending SMS notifications. We do not collect any other personal information beyond what is necessary to deliver messages.

## 2. How We Use Your Information

Phone numbers collected by Polly-App are used solely to send SMS text message notifications (such as reminders, alerts, or updates) on behalf of the authorized organization. We do not use your phone number for marketing purposes.

## 3. How We Share Your Information

We do not sell, rent, or share your phone number or any personal information with third parties, except as necessary to deliver SMS messages (e.g., our SMS service provider, Twilio). Twilio's privacy policy can be found at https://www.twilio.com/en-us/legal/privacy.

## 4. Data Retention

Phone numbers are retained only as long as necessary to provide the notification service. You may request removal of your information at any time by contacting us at abrahamborg@gmail.com.

## 5. Opt-Out

You may opt out of receiving SMS messages at any time by replying **STOP** to any message you receive from us. After opting out, you will receive no further messages. To opt back in, reply **START**.

## 6. Message and Data Rates

Standard message and data rates may apply to SMS messages you receive. Contact your mobile carrier for details.

## 7. Security

We take reasonable measures to protect the information we collect from unauthorized access, disclosure, or misuse.

## 8. Children's Privacy

Polly-App operates in educational environments and complies with applicable laws regarding the privacy of minors. Phone numbers for minors are only collected with proper authorization from the relevant school, district, or parent/guardian, as required by applicable law.

## 9. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be reflected by an updated Effective Date at the top of this page.

## 10. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:  
abrahamborg@gmail.com
